611
00:40:43,567 --> 00:40:44,610
You love sharks?

612
00:40:44,693 --> 00:40:46,028
Yeah, I love them.

613
00:40:46,112 --> 00:40:48,364
When I was 12 years old,
my father got me a boat

614
00:40:48,447 --> 00:40:50,199
