I heard it on the Cape station.

630
00:41:28,737 --> 00:41:31,323
They caught a shark,
not the shark.

631
00:41:31,824 --> 00:41:34,410
Not the shark that
killed Chrissie Watkins.

632
00:41:34,618 --> 00:41:37,288
