by cutting the shark open...

634
00:41:40,249 --> 00:41:43,335
You may want to let
that breathe... Nothing.

635
00:41:59,935 --> 00:42:03,272
You know, you'll be
the only rational man

636
00:42:03,355 --> 00:42:05,065
left on this island
after I leave tomorrow.

637
00:42:05,774 --> 00:42:07,318
