638
00:42:08,611 --> 00:42:10,362
<i>I am going
on the Aurora.</i>

639
00:42:10,446 --> 00:42:11,864
The Aurora?
What is that?

640
00:42:11,947 --> 00:42:14,867
It's a floating asylum
for shark addicts.

641
00:42:14,950 --> 00:42:16,994
