Rogue.

657
00:42:57,534 --> 00:42:58,953
Rogue, yeah.

658
00:42:59,411 --> 00:43:02,498
This guy,
he keeps swimming around

659
00:43:02,581 --> 00:43:04,375
in a place where
the feeding is good

660
00:43:04,458 --> 00:43:06,335
until the food
supply is gone, right?

661
00:43:06,418 --> 00:43:07,920
