territoriality.

662
00:43:08,003 --> 00:43:11,257
It's just a theory that
I happen to agree with.

663
00:43:13,842 --> 00:43:15,427
Then why don't we
have one more drink

664
00:43:15,511 --> 00:43:18,013
and go down
and cut that shark open?

665
00:43:18,514 --> 00:43:21,225
