threw that in the river.

680
00:44:31,795 --> 00:44:33,547
(PANTING)

681
00:44:37,801 --> 00:44:39,178
That's it.

682
00:44:41,013 --> 00:44:44,099
I've got to close the
beach, call the Mayor.

683
