mostly myself, actually.

717
00:46:15,858 --> 00:46:17,651
You're kidding.
No.

718
00:46:18,318 --> 00:46:19,987
You rich?
Yeah.

719
00:46:20,779 --> 00:46:22,156
How much?

720
00:46:22,239 --> 00:46:23,740
